<div class="item-content">
<h3><a href="https://calwatchdog.com/2013/03/15/businesses-protest-gov-browns-fee-hike/">Businesses protest Gov. Brown’s fee hike</a></h3>
<p>March 15, 2013 By Dave Roberts “Constantly expanding the coercive power of government by adding each year so many minute</p>
</div>
</div>
